These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, september
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, game
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, sports
1. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the chaman-smoker##5
3. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Transport      | ship     | motorbike      |
| Birthday          | september | may    |
| Cigar         | game   | chaman |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, dog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, basketball
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, purple
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
3. the person who likes purple is not to the right of the person who likes lilac##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's sport is basketball##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Pet    | goat        | dog    |
| Sport       | ice-hockey         | basketball |
| Color         | purple | lilac   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
City: marseilles, liverpool
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, architect
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the right of the architect##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | chess |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| City   | marseilles | liverpool |
| Job           | musician        | architect   |

